B.Wh=s(["Both are turned ON","One is ON and one is OFF","Both are turned OFF","The position does not matter"],t.s)
B.a8k=new A.a0(-101,B.ay,607,"During wet motoring, what is the position of the ignition systems?",B.Wh,2,B.C,null,null,null)
B.Yg=s(["Engine speed only","The starter motor temperature","The exhaust nozzle for signs of fuel","The HP rotor vibration"],t.s)
