B.Ml=new A.al("Refer to the CMM for detailed overhaul procedures. NDT inspection is required at every major check.","Detayl\u0131 revizyon prosed\xfcrleri i\xe7in CMM'ye bak\u0131n. Her b\xfcy\xfck bak\u0131mda NDT muayenesi gereklidir.","CMM \u2026 NDT")
